cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new way of thinking about deep neural networks from a probabilistic perspective, which is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the construction of models for computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and the proposed framework sheds light on the functionality of neural networks (cs.NE).
